NUMBER 2586
NAME Mausoleum, inside
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
REGION 11
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A single sarchophagus lies, open, in the center of the mausoleum floor.
Its lid has been cast to the far corner of the room, lying there, amongst
the cobwebs, in many shattered pieces. A few blackened torch holders hang
crookedly off the walls. A single arch leads back outside to the graveyard.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 60 VAL2=2585
ITEM 1 234
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Beneath a fine layer of dust and cobwebs on the side of the sarcophagus is
some scrawled writing.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 1
         "My task is done, to Shemri's Realm I go,"
         "The offspring of the cat, hidden and safe."
*DESCRIPTION_END
