  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR INTNUM45 = 0
    IFVAR ARCHNUM = 117
      IFVAR ITEMADJ2 = 241
        REMOVEITEM -1
         ECHO PLAYER The mouth of the skeleton closes around your offering and when it opens again the pearl is gone. The skeleton's eyes flash momentarily and then it begins to speak in a soft whisper...
         ECHO PLAYER "Pieces of Eight,"
         ECHO PLAYER "Found only by the bright."
         ECHO PLAYER "Long road to riches,"
         ECHO PLAYER "Don't get to big for your britches,"
         ECHO PLAYER "Only the first step you have taken,"
	 ECHO PLAYER "Before the gods of treasure you can awaken."
         ECHO OTHERS %N places a polished pearl within the skeletons mouth, which closes around the offering, and an immediate wind springs up muffling all sounds due to its mournful intensity.
         EQUAL INTNUM45 1
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
