NUMBER 2617
NAME Jungle Edge
JUNGLE
DAY_LIGHT
REGION 11
ITEM 9 693
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Masses of deep emerald vines, tall narrow fronded palms and a bountiful array
of bushes display almost any shade of green imaginable. Brillant fist-sized
scarlet blossoms exude a sweet scent and tiny brillant orange blooms glisten
with a thick clear liquid, both providing an attraction for the many winged
insects which flit between them. Smooth barked green-wooded logs lie atop
mounds of sloughed off leaves while older aged leafless carcasses are tangled
and overgrown by the ever encroaching jungle. A narrow path continues on
to the northeast.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT SE 2616
EXIT NE 2618
ITEM 1 196 ADJ1=297
ITEM 2 664 ADJ1=87 ADJ2=152
MONSTER_GROUP 102
  IFVERB TOUCH 2
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER The broad leaves feel slick and smooth.
    ECHO OTHERS %N runs %h fingers over one of the vines.
  ENDIF
IFVERB SNIFF 1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER A sweet fruity aroma assaults your nostrils lingering for a moment before fading away.
  ECHO OTHERS As %N sniffs a large fragrant bloom a pleasant smile crosses %h face.
ENDIF
  IFVERB LISTEN -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER The hum of busy insects fills the air.
    ECHO OTHERS %N swats aimlessly at the air.
  ENDIF
VARIABLE tropic2
IFVERB SEARCH -1
   IFVAR TIM ! TROPIC2
     RANDOM dummy1 1 100 0
     ADD dummy1 PER
       IFVAR dummy1 => 175
         ECHO PLAYER You find a low growing blossom and pluck it from its stem.
         ECHO OTHERS %N found something in the bushes!
           IFITEM 8
             REMOVEITEM 8
             NEWITEM 8 1143 ADJ1=90 ADJ2=259
	   ENDIF
           IFNOITEM 8
             NEWITEM 8 1143 ADJ1=90 ADJ2=259
           ENDIF
           EQUAL tropic2 TIM
       ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
